"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-news-weird-1935473-olympic-torch-found-tiktok\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  TheOlympictorch is an important symbol of unity for any country hosting the international sporting event.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 107, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It travels around the country before igniting the flame at the opening ceremony and is uniquely designed for each games.\", \"from\": 109, \"to\": 229, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This year, the Paris 2024 Games chose to work with French designer Mathieu Lehanneur to create a water-inspired design.\", \"from\": 230, \"to\": 349, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 281, \"end\": 287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9968912323463122, \"rank\": 0.0029916768359918287, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But back in 2012, London went with a golden torch designed by designers BarberOsgerby, which was perforated by 8000 circular holes representing each of the torch-bearers to take part in the relay.\", \"from\": 351, \"to\": 547, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 369, \"end\": 375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999956370868082, \"rank\": 2.9926874999883018e-06, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 423, \"end\": 436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barber_Osgerby\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BarberOsgerby\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barber_Osgerby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barber_Osgerby\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no way you could not spot it from a mile away - even in the most unexpected of places.\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 643, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One bloke was recently left baffled when he and his pal found a London torch at a train station inWandsworth Common, London.\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 709, \"end\": 715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999956370868082, \"rank\": 2.9926874999883018e-06, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a video, which has gained more than 15,000 likes, the lad who posts as@younisecrets, said: \\\"Guys, I was just standing on this platform and I saw this.\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 924, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought it was part of the bench at first, but tell me this is not what I think it is, bro.\\\"\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 1019, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"wot do we do with this SEND HELP#olympics2024#olympics  He then showed the London Olympics logo on the side before panning the camera around to show the empty platform.\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1189, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1096, \"end\": 1111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999985370778, \"rank\": 1.095319657424858e-09, \"text\": \"London Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His pal added: \\\"Oh my God, it's like a f*****g official one.\\\"\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1251, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To which, he replied: \\\"Is it real?\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1287, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What do we do?\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1302, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Literally, no one's here,\\\" before adding in the caption: \\\"Wot do we do with this SEND HELP.\\\"\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1395, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TikTokusers have been left stunned over the find as some joked that they will have to organise the next Olympics because they found it.\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1532, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One user joked: \\\"I think that means you are now hosting the next Olympics, so good luck with that!\\\"\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1632, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1743, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1820, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1853, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Another added: \\\"Surely you have got to keep that,\\\" as a third quipped: \\\"I think this is an original experience.\\\"\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1990, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, someone else penned: \\\"I have been obsessed with the London Olympic torch since I was a kid.\", \"from\": 1991, \"to\": 2093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2054, \"end\": 2060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999956370868082, \"rank\": 2.9926874999883018e-06, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why does this s*** never happen to me?\\\"\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Representatives for the Olympics have been contacted for a comment.\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2202, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2373, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2341, \"end\": 2354, \"title\": \"h